<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.7.3">
<l>cāntamum pūṇuñ cantaṉak kuḻampun taṭamulaik kaṇiyilun taḻalām</l>
<l>pōntaveṇ tiṅkaḷ katircuṭa meliyum porukaṭal pulampilum pulampum</l>
<l>māntaḷir mēṉi vaṇṇamum poṉṉām vaḷaikaḷu miṟainillā veṉtaṉ</l>
<l>ēntiḻai yivaḷuk keṉṉiṉain tiruntā yiṭaventai yentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If  she puts jewels, powders, or sandal paste on her broad breasts,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will burn.</l>
<l>As the beams of the seemly, silvery moon burn, she grows thin;</l>
<l rend="indent">and if the crashing sea moans, she moans.</l>
<l>The color of her body is sallow [like] a mango shoot;</l>
<l rend="indent">the bangles on her arms will not stay</l>
<l>What were you intending for my own bejeweled girl, lord father of Iṭaventai?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
